description: After a decade as a closet geek and departmental guru, David LaGesse started writing about personal tech for U.S. News six years ago. He also writes about corporate trends, strategies and executives, having spent more than a decade as a business writer at newspapers including most recently The Dallas Morning News, where he also spent seven years covering Latin American affairs.
